## PART 3: HIGHER EDUCATION (NQF Levels 5-10)

### 3.1 NQF Level 5 - Higher Certificates

**Duration:** 1-3 years (120 credits)  
**Entry:** NSC/ASC with APS 15+ OR RPL for 23+ with experience  
**Exam-Only via UNISA:** ✅ Yes - Online assessments

**UNISA Examples (Business & Management):**
- Higher Certificate in Accounting Sciences (98201)
- Higher Certificate in Banking (98225)
- Higher Certificate in Economic & Management Sciences (98237)
- Higher Certificate in Marketing
- Higher Certificate in Retailing
- Higher Certificate in Supervisory Management

**UNISA Examples (Law & Public Service):**
- Higher Certificate in Law (98751)
- Higher Certificate in Criminal Justice (90006)

**UNISA Examples (Education):**
- Higher Certificate in Education: Foundation & Intermediate Phase (90093)
- Higher Certificate in Education: Senior Phase Maths & Science

**UNISA Examples (Sciences):**
- Higher Certificate in Mathematics & Statistics (90129)
- Higher Certificate in Physical Sciences (90101)

**UNISA Examples (Other):**
- Higher Certificate in Animal Welfare (90098)
- Higher Certificate in Archives & Records Management (98577)
- Higher Certificate in Tourism Management

**Cost per Module:** R1,815-R3,000  
**Total Certificate Cost:** R22,000-R36,000

