**Duration:** 1 year full-time (120 credits)  
**Entry:** Bachelor's degree (minimum 60-65%)  
**Exam-Only via UNISA:** ✅ Yes

**Available in ALL undergraduate fields:**
- Honours in Accounting Sciences (Management/Financial/Internal Audit/Taxation)
- Honours in Business Management
- Honours in Economics
