- Postgraduate Diploma in Accounting (CTA route to CA(SA))
- Postgraduate Diploma in Business Administration
- Postgraduate Diploma in Education
- Postgraduate Diploma in Financial Accounting
- Postgraduate Diploma in Management
- Postgraduate Diploma in Disability Studies

**UNISA Honours Costs:**
- **Per Module:** R2,805-R4,000
- **Total Honours:** R25,000-R35,000

