### 3.5 NQF Level 9 - Master's Degrees

**Duration:** 1-2 years (coursework) | 2-3 years (research)  
**Entry:** Honours/4-year bachelor's (60-65%+)  
**Credits:** 180-240

**Types:**
1. **Coursework Masters:** Structured modules + mini-dissertation
2. **Research Masters:** Full dissertation (90-180 credits)
3. **Professional Masters:** MBA, M.Ed, LLM, MCom, etc.

**Available in ALL academic disciplines!**

**Popular Professional Masters:**
- MBA (Master of Business Administration)
- M.Ed (Master of Education) - various specializations
- LLM (Master of Laws) - specialization fields
- MCom (various business fields)
- MA (all humanities fields)
- MSc (all science fields)
- M.Tech (various technical fields)

**UNISA Masters Costs:**
- **Coursework Module:** R2,900-R5,795/year
- **Research Registration:** R5,795/year
- **Total Masters:** R30,000-R80,000

**Exam-Only:** ✅ Partial - Coursework yes, research unavoidable

---

### 3.6 NQF Level 10 - Doctoral Degrees

**Duration:** 3-5+ years minimum  
**Entry:** Master's degree  
**Structure:** Original research + thesis/dissertation (360 credits minimum)

**Types:**
- **PhD (Doctor of Philosophy)** - Traditional research doctorate in ANY field
- **Professional Doctorates:** DBA (Business Admin), DEd (Education), D.Litt et Phil, DTech

**Exam-Only:** ❌ Requires original research, publications, thesis defense

**UNISA Doctorate Costs:**
- **Annual Registration:** ~R5,795-R10,000/year
- **Total (3-5 years):** R20,000-R60,000 (excluding research costs)

**Available Fields:** ALL academic disciplines from Part 3.3

