- ChatGPT Free (OpenAI)
- Gemini Free (Google)
- Llama via HuggingFace Chat
- DeepSeek Free Tier
- Perplexity Free
- Microsoft Copilot (Bing)

**Education-Specific:**
- Khan Academy (with AI tutor)
- Socratic by Google
- Photomath (mathematics)
- Duolingo (languages)

### 6.3 Study Strategy: AI + Exam-Only

**Phase 1: Content Mastery (60% of time)**
- Use AI for explanations, examples, practice problems
- Work through entire syllabus systematically
- Create flashcards with AI assistance
- Generate quiz questions from curriculum

**Phase 2: Practice & Application (30% of time)**
- Past exam papers (download from DBE/IEB/UNISA)
- AI feedback on practice answers
- Weak area identification
- Targeted revision with AI tutoring

**Phase 3: Exam Preparation (10% of time)**
- Timed practice exams
- Exam technique with AI coaching
- Final revision
- Confidence building

**Resources:**
- **Past Papers:** education.gov.za, ieb.co.za, myUnisa portal
- **Curricula:** CAPS documents (DBE website)
- **Study Guides:** AI-generated from syllabus
- **Practice Questions:** AI-generated unlimited questions

